data.description: Price Improved and a 5K Seller Contribution toward Buyer's Closing Costs!! Welcome home to 260 Coconut Palm Pkwy! Step inside & discover a great floor plan that offers style, functionality & upgrades galore! This is an ideal place to call home! The gourmet kitchen features upgraded cabinetry, quartz countertops, a gas cooktop, double ovens, a farm sink, an oversized wood shelving walk in pantry shelving with an appliance station, & more! The heart of the home is the Great Room where conversations flow easily from the kitchen to the cozy living room. This room features a beautiful stone fireplace wall, surrounded by custom wood shelving & a detailed coffered ceiling overhead. The disappearing Triple Sliders lead to outside to a spacious screened in lanai & an outdoor trex-deck with a preserve view & fenced yard! The expanded Primary Suite is a true retreat featuring a beautiful custom accent wall, bay windows overlooking the private preserve, trey ceilings, 2 walk-in closets, a large en-suite bathroom with dual vanities, a huge walk-in shower & a stand-alone tub! Additional rooms include an office space with built in shelving, a separate dining room with butler area, a laundry room with a countertop and storage cabinets, & a large bonus room that can be a bedroom, a second family room, a game room, etc. You decide! Additional features include a 3-car garage, LVP throughout, fenced yard, tankless gas water heater, water softener, a ring video doorbell, & it's piped for gas to add on an outdoor kitchen! Come enjoy the Nocatee lifestyle in this golf cart friendly community with resort-style amenities including, pools, water parks, greenway trails, kayak launches, sports courts and fields, planned community events, shopping, restaurants and more!
